Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.51,0:00:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything this world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.66,0:00:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:35.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:40.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:47.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:52.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:16.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.21,0:01:21.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:25.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:30.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:36.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:42.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:47.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:51.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:53.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:58.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna rescue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:06.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge is coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:16.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:24.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:26.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:31.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nami would never kill Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:37.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who're friends, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:38.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:40.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:44.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?\NYou're our friend! We came to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:47.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:50.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Friends? Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:55.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a pathetic bunch of\Npeople cooperating with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:03:03.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"A Bond of Friendship Woven\Nby Tears! Nami's World Map"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:18.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You really know how to trash a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:24.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I'm just here to rest a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:32.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking glass and furniture\Njust to rest is a bit much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:36.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have that treasure map open,\Neven though nothing's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:40.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened to make me mad, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Them, huh? Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:44.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You met them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Some Captain Something-or-Other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:51.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He seemed kind of liar-ish, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:56.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you smiled happily when\Nyou were traveling with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:04:02.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I haven't\Nseen you like that in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:08.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me! Who are those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:16.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We agreed you could tell\Nme anything, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:25.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I had planned to forget about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:29.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had erased them from my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:37.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you take your friends for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:05:02.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly felt like always being\Nwith them, if it were possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that'd hit you hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:20.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To think that someone\Nreally showed up for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:24.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:32.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The most painful word for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:40.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, girlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:46.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to return\Nthe village that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:50.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then how's this? Let's make an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:53.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:56.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gather up 100 million Berries and bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:06:00.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do so and I'll let the village\Ngo and give you freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Honest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:03.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:07.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'd die before I'd break an\Nagreement concerning money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:15.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how many years\Nit takes. I'll honor our agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:20.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely will save up 100 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:24.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:32.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's wrong, skilled surveyor\Nof ours? Why the angry look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:37.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy men you have under\Nyour control stole all my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:42.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to dying before\Nbreaking promises about money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:46.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When did I break our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:51.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb! You teamed\Nup with the Navy to--!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:59.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When did I break our promise? Let's hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:09.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you... Damn you! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:14.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So your money's been stolen?\NHow unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:16.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But an agreement is an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:19.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't gather up\N100 million Berries for me to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:25.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I can't give you the village back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:29.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:37.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's only 100 million Berries!\NJust start saving up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:41.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you gonna run out on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:49.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But if you do run away, I'll kill\Neveryone in Cocoyashi Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:51.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:54.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We pretended we didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because our hopes would keep you\Nfrom running away from Arlong
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:05.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,if you ever decided to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No more of this! Take up\Nyour weapons! Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:14.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eight years ago, we swore\Nnot to throw away our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:17.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how painful and insulting\Nit was to be ruled by them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:22.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we swore to fight the patient fight\Nas long as Nami was cheerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:25.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But this is their answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:29.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now that our village's chance for\Nfreedom is gone, we have no hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:31.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,More than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:35.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we must make those fishmen pay\Nfor toying with that girl's kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:36.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Any objections?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:39.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:43.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:48.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:53.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more! Just wait a\Nlittle more! I'll work hard again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:55.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save up the money again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:57.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be easy this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:09:02.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it! I'll be fine!\NThere's no need to worry at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:07.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing compared to back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:09.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please, no more dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:17.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! I'm fine! I'm just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:22.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:25.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even you know there's no point now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:30.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You fought very well, carrying our\Nlives on your back all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:33.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Joining them must've been\Neven more painful for you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:37.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,than being cut through the heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:41.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You fought very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:48.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:52.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the village now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:55.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:57.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nacchan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:00.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:04.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're crafty, and you have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:07.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nojiko! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:16.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, everyone! I don't want to\Nsee anyone else get hurt by them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:27.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:34.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! We've made up our minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:38.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of our way, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:39.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:47.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't win,\Nlet's show 'em what we're made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:29.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong! Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong! Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:39.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:45.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:49.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!\NYou don't even know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:53.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know what's happened\Non this island the past eight years!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:55.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:58.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:01.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, leave the damn island already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:05.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Leave! I don't need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:09.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Leave! Leave! Leave! Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:12.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Leave! Leave! Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:20.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:37.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:45.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:59.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:04.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:12.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:24.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:37.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:45.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of you is Arlong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can no longer escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:03.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the top floor of Arlong Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:05.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:06.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Full of papers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:09.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These're not just ordinary papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:14.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This room is where I make that\Nwoman draw sea charts. It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:16.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...the survey room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nami's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:22.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These're all sea charts that Nami drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:28.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to continue drawing\Nsea charts! For my ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:32.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And once her charts give me full\Nknowledge of all the world's seas...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:38.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...we fishmen will be invincible,\Nand the world will become our empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:45.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our first stepping stone is\Nthis island... and the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:52.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could you use the girl as efficiently as that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:56.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Use"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:59.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:02.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:06.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:14.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What in the...?! There's an\Nawful lot of stuff flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:24.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:27.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The charts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:35.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,M-My charts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:40.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This... is a pretty intense fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:43.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Looks like a fight to the death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:51.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:16:00.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:16.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone too far, you damn rubber man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:23.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Fishmen are great" and "sea charts" this,\N"circumstances" that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:26.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about any of that stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:34.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I finally figured out how to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:39.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She can't go because this room is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:45.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't want to be here,\Nthen I'll just destroy it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:49.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:57.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...Battle-Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:08.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! It's gonna collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:11.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is dangerous! Everyone, get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Nami! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:14.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Luffy's still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:21.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,--Big Sis!\N--Luffy! Luffy's still...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:29.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:35.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:37.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which one won?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:41.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Given all this debris... Don't tell me it was--!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:49.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:58.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:06.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:18.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is he okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:27.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:37.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:49.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:53.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My friends helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:57.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll fight for one of my friends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:19:02.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, Robin, have faith in us... in Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:07.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He'll respond to your feelings without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:15.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pirates! What're you\Nguys wasting time for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:26.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the meaning of that smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:28.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:33.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:40.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Straw Hat Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Part 3"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Obahan: Middle-aged Woman]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the Straw Hats were\Nall middle-aged women..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:20:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...who would be the strongest?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffizaki"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:05.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear! I'm out of soy sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:07.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was gonna make\Nsoy sauce meat steak,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:07.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,meat salad and meat miso soup today...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:10.72,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Today's menu\Nsoy sauce meat steak\Nmeat salad (no veggies) \Nmeat miso soup (without soup)"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:12.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, I'm coming in, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:14.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoroyama-san, I'm out of soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:18.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, be a dearie and spare\Nme some, would you? Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:21.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That gave me a start!\NHey, are you in the middle of training?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:23.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dearie me, if it isn't Luffizaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:27.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, no, I'm not training.\NWe're having sashimi today...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:29.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...so I was just cutting some raw fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:31.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, seems like you cut the whole kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:33.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, soy sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're... all out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, your bottle's been cut in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Supermarket Isoflavone"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, you can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:43.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my word... My word...!\NThis ham is the bee's knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This one with the cheese wrapped\Nin ham is simply to die for!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:47.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be a dear and get me some jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:47.38,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sampling"\N"Half Price"\N"Ham"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:51.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, you can't bring rice\Ninto the sampling section!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:54.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Come now,\NLuffizaki-san does this all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:56.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's always causing us trouble, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:59.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can it! Now bring me some\Nsweet jam for this ham!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:02.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Make it sweet and tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:05.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's the grabby fiend, Sanjida!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:09.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, my! Just what is the problem?\NWe're all ladies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:13.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Let me touch your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:16.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,--Enough of that, you two!\N--Oh, no, Mellorine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:19.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good! It's the middle-aged woman\Nof once-a-month justice, Namijima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:21.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She forgets her own faults and tells off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:26.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the middle-aged woman pirate gang\Nonce a month for some reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:29.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:31.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Luffizaki-san!\NHave I got news for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:33.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The supermarket in front of the train\Nstation has some super bargains!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:34.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The meat is freakin' cheap, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:36.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Meat is?! Usokawa-san,\Nyou aren't fooling me, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:37.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was lying. I brought you the circular.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:38.43,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Circular"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:40.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, phooey!\N--But forget that, I have terrible news!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:43.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chopamori-san and Sanjida-san\Nwere caught at the supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:47.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,--Ah, I need some tea!\N--Oh, dear! Could it be that\NNamijima-san is at it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:50.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:54.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Robino-san! Let us hide here!\NNamijima-san's gonna kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.05,0:21:56.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:59.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've been warning you guys\Nabout sorting your trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:03.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop insisting that\Neverything is burnable trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:05.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that nonsense?!\NIt's burnable if there's enough spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:07.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why, good point, Luffizaki-san! She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:09.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a matter of spirit... The incinerator's.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:10.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What silly nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.95,0:22:12.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Pickled vegetables?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:15.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your pickled vegetables are\Nthe best, Robino-san! I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:21.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! Then let's take a break and have\Nthis barley tea I found in the fridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.09,0:22:23.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.12,0:22:25.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:27.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why, yes, they're here. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Robino-san? Who just called?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:36.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Namijima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:39.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So... mind telling me what\Nhappened to this month's rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.64,0:22:41.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Big landowner, Namijima-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:44.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could you be a dearie and wait\Nuntil tomorrow's town raffle event?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:49.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm gonna go to your employers\Nand collect the money directly from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:52.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, Namijima-san! Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:54.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is gonna mark the end of our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:22:58.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,--Fine by me.\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.28,0:23:00.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they're all middle-aged women,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.58,0:23:08.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the strongest one is Namijima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:14.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Robin has been alone all this time...\Njust like I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:17.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But our paths crossed and we became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.43,0:23:19.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone anymore, Robin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:21.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. You've got Luffy and all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.35,0:23:23.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna let\Nanyone sacrifice themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:24.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:26.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We'll rescue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:27.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:31.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Parting Builds a Man's Character!\NSanji and Chopper"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:39.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
